First of all, her W has bugged me a little bit, I don&#039;t know if it&#039;s more than it should but it does. Her W specifically says that it can be used on a target &quot;Enemy Minion&quot;, but it also works on Neutral Monsters. It only bothers me because a few champions that I don&#039;t remember off hand, maybe Nunu, says both enemy minions, and Neutral Monsters. I wanted to see if that could be fixed anytime soon if possible.

Second of all, I would really love to see a Dunkmaster Syndra skin as a sequel to the Dunkmaster Darius skin. I mean that would be a pretty awesome skin :DDD{{champion:134}} 

Thanks for reading Riot, and I hope you can get to it soon if at all :DD~!
